370
00:41:41,200 --> 00:41:45,300
Is it about Felix?
Are you calling about my son?

371
00:41:46,100 --> 00:41:51,000
Up at Oil Derrick 22, in the Baldwin
Hills, there are some bushes.

372
00:41:53,100 --> 00:41:57,000
