- Let me talk to your boss.

386
00:44:57,400 --> 00:45:00,100
I said...
- Don't make me mad, boy.

387
00:45:00,400 --> 00:45:03,000
You can't work here,
unless you have a phone.

388
00:45:03,400 --> 00:45:08,600
