402
00:46:43,800 --> 00:46:46,700
but I think I know where
I might be able to find him.

403
00:47:00,000 --> 00:47:01,900
What's wrong?

404
00:47:06,000 --> 00:47:08,100
I am scared.

405
00:47:11,100 --> 00:47:14,100
So if you really could help me,
I wish you would.

406
00:47:17,000 --> 00:47:19,100
